divs: sighting detailsi had stepped out side w\o camera and noticed a light not quite a pulse, but not a strobe. the object was not a known aircraft to me. it was slowly moving w to east and approaching sun glare. after retrieving camera, 10 sec. or less i was not able to spot the object. i shot 10-12 quick shots in the general area that i thought it would be, and captured in 1 frame, which i am including.
